Release and security surfaces.

## Mandatory

Before ship / TestFlight / notarization discussions → launch **`security-privacy-scanner`** via `Task`.

## Skills

- macOS DMG / notarization: `build-macos-apps:packaging-notarization`, `build-macos-apps:signing-entitlements`
- iOS TestFlight: `axiom:axiom-shipping` + [`docs/reference/release-readiness.md`](../../docs/reference/release-readiness.md)
- GitHub release workflow: `github:github`, `github:gh-fix-ci`

## CI boundary

Scoped to macOS release packaging + iOS compile-safety only (`.github/workflows/release.yml`). Do not reintroduce test bundles or extra workflows without maintainer decision.

Playbook: [`.cursor/rules/vocello-agent-playbook.mdc`](vocello-agent-playbook.mdc)
